OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1771879288
OL,3,CVape shop which 'routinely sold
OL,4,Cillicit vapes' to underage teens
OL,5,Cshutdown
OL,7,FA vape shop that "routinely sold
OL,8,Fillicit vapes" to teenagers has been
OL,9,Fordered to shut after failing two test
OL,10,Fpurchases.
OL,12,FFallowfield Mini Mart, on Platt Lane
OL,13,Fin Manchester, was first investigated
OL,14,Fafter allegations arose it was selling
OL,15,Fchildren vapes alongside making
OL,16,Fillicit tobacco available for
OL,17,Fpurchase, in March 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
