PN,39402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1771879288
OL,3,CVape shop which 'routinely sold
OL,4,Cillicit vapes' to underage teens
OL,5,Cshutdown
OL,7,FA month later a test purchase was
OL,8,Fcarried out where a volunteer underage
OL,9,Fcustomer was able to purchase a vape
OL,10,Ffrom the shop.
OL,12,FAfter the initial investigation,
OL,13,FTrading Standards officers raided the
OL,14,Fshop, confiscating tens of thousands
OL,15,Fof cigarettes, hand-rolling tobacco
OL,16,Fand more than 100 illegal vapes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1771879288
OL,3,CVape shop which 'routinely sold
OL,4,Cillicit vapes' to underage teens
OL,5,Cshutdown
OL,7,FDespite ongoing warnings about the
OL,8,Fillegality of these practices, the
OL,9,Fshop continued to break the law, and a
OL,10,Fsecond test purchase in July 2025
OL,11,Fagain saw an underage volunteer
OL,12,Fsuccessfully buy a vape.
OL,14,FAnother Trading Standards visit in
OL,15,FAugust 2025 resulted in the seizure of
OL,16,F5,200 cigarettes, 1.2kg of hand-
OL,17,Frolling tobacco, and 37 non-compliant
OL,18,Fvapes for non-compliance.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1771879288
OL,3,CVape shop which 'routinely sold
OL,4,Cillicit vapes' to underage teens
OL,5,Cshutdown
OL,7,FFaced with continued violations and a
OL,8,Flack of cooperation from the shop
OL,9,Fowners, the Council decided to pursue
OL,10,Fa closure order, which was issued by
OL,11,FMagistrates' Court on Wednesday, 18
OL,12,FFebruary.
OL,14,FThe Closure Order prevents Fallowfield
OL,15,FMini Mart from reopening for three
OL,16,Fmonths, until 17 May 2026.
OL,18,FAdditionally, the court ordered the
OL,19,Fowner and director of the shop to pay
OL,20,Fthe Council's legal costs, totalling
OL,21,F#3,037.76.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
