PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1771879288
OL,3,CVape shop which 'routinely sold
OL,4,Cillicit vapes' to underage teens
OL,5,Cshutdown
OL,7,FManchester City Council, said "This
OL,8,Fresult is a win for the local
OL,9,Fcommunity who has for too long been
OL,10,Fimpacted by the illegal actions linked
OL,11,Fto this premises.
OL,13,F"Laws against the sale of illicit
OL,14,Fvapes and tobacco products are in
OL,15,Fplace to protect our residents.
OL,26,@oD@_OUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
