CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1771879288
OL,3,CVape shop which 'routinely sold
OL,4,Cillicit vapes' to underage teens
OL,5,Cshutdown
OL,7,F"In Manchester we have some of the
OL,8,Fworst health outcomes when it comes to
OL,9,Fsmoking-related illnesses, and the
OL,10,Fsale of these products makes it harder
OL,11,Ffor people to quit, and easier for new
OL,12,Fsmokers to take up the habit."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
